<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/public.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="public-container">
        <div class="public-header">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
            <p>How we handle your location data</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content-section">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>When you participate in our location tracking demonstration, we collect:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Location Data:</strong> GPS coordinates (latitude, longitude)</li>
                    <li><strong>Accuracy Information:</strong> How precise the location data is</li>
                    <li><strong>Timestamps:</strong> When each location update was recorded</li>
                    <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Browser type, operating system, screen resolution</li>
                    <li><strong>Network Information:</strong> IP address, connection type</li>
                    <li><strong>Battery Information:</strong> Battery level (if available)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>Your information is used solely for:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Educational demonstration of location tracking technology</li>
                    <li>Showing real-time location updates to authorized users</li>
                    <li>Analyzing accuracy and reliability of location data</li>
                    <li>Improving our educational materials</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>3. Data Storage and Security</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Temporary Storage:</strong> Data is stored temporarily for demonstration purposes</li>
                    <li><strong>Automatic Deletion:</strong> All data is automatically deleted after 24 hours</li>
                    <li><strong>Secure Database:</strong> Data is stored in a secure MongoDB database</li>
                    <li><strong>No Persistent Storage:</strong> We do not keep permanent records of your location</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>4. Consent and Control</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Explicit Consent:</strong> We always ask for your permission before tracking</li>
                    <li><strong>Opt-out Anytime:</strong> You can stop tracking by closing the browser tab</li>
                    <li><strong>No Coercion:</strong> Participation is completely voluntary</li>
                    <li><strong>Clear Information:</strong> We explain what data we collect and why</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
                <p>We do not share your location data with:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Third-party companies</li>
                    <li>Advertisers</li>
                    <li>Government agencies (unless legally required)</li>
                    <li>Other users (except the session creator for educational purposes)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>You have the right to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Access:</strong> Know what data we have about you</li>
                    <li><strong>Delete:</strong> Request immediate deletion of your data</li>
                    <li><strong>Withdraw:</strong> Stop tracking at any time</li>
                    <li><strong>Question:</strong> Ask about our data practices</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>7. Legal Basis</h2>
                <p>We process your location data based on:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Consent:</strong> You explicitly agree to location tracking</li>
                    <li><strong>Educational Purpose:</strong> Legitimate interest in education and demonstration</li>
                    <li><strong>Limited Scope:</strong> Data collection is minimal and temporary</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
                <p>This service is not intended for children under 13. We do not knowingly collect location data from children.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>9. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy to reflect changes in our practices. Users will be notified of any significant changes.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="info-card">
                <h2>10. Contact Information</h2>
                <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy or our data practices, please contact us.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>⚠️ Disclaimer</h3>
                <p>This application is for educational purposes only. Location tracking without consent is illegal in many jurisdictions. Always ensure you have proper authorization before tracking anyone's location.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="privacy-links">
            <a href="/about">About This Tool</a>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
